{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/bcit-ci/CodeIgniter/issues/6201","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/bcit-ci/CodeIgniter","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/bcit-ci/CodeIgniter/issues/6201/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/bcit-ci/CodeIgniter/issues/6201/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/bcit-ci/CodeIgniter/issues/6201/events","html_url":"https://github.com/bcit-ci/CodeIgniter/issues/6201","id":1628890691,"node_id":"I_kwDOACIW9s5hFuZD","number":6201,"title":"Pagination::create_links() not compatible with PHP 8.1","user":{"login":"daveherman71","id":20796097,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjIwNzk2MDk3","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/20796097?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/daveherman71","html_url":"https://github.com/daveherman71","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/daveherman71/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/daveherman71/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/daveherman71/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/daveherman71/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/daveherman71/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/daveherman71/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/daveherman71/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/daveherman71/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/daveherman71/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"labels":[{"id":140924,"node_id":"MDU6TGFiZWwxNDA5MjQ=","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/bcit-ci/CodeIgniter/labels/Bug","name":"Bug","color":"eb2420","default":false,"description":null}],"state":"closed","locked":false,"assignee":null,"assignees":[],"milestone":null,"comments":0,"created_at":"2023-03-17T08:17:38Z","updated_at":"2023-03-21T23:28:51Z","closed_at":"2023-03-21T23:28:42Z","author_association":"NONE","type":null,"active_lock_reason":null,"sub_issues_summary":{"total":0,"completed":0,"percent_completed":0},"issue_dependencies_summary":{"blocked_by":0,"total_blocked_by":0,"blocking":0,"total_blocking":0},"body":"An error occurs in the pagination library when calling the `create_links()` method when the value of the current page is not present in the URL. This is a likely possibility when viewing page 1 of a dataset.\r\n\r\n```\r\nA PHP Error was encountered\r\nSeverity: 8192\r\nMessage: ctype_digit(): Argument of type null will be interpreted as string in the future\r\nFilename: libraries/Pagination.php\r\nLine Number: 518\r\n```\r\n\r\nLine 518 is as follows:\r\n\r\n```\r\nif ( ! ctype_digit($this->cur_page) OR ($this->use_page_numbers && (int) $this->cur_page === 0))\r\n```\r\n\r\nThe reason the error occurs is because at this point the value of `$this->cur_page` is NULL.\r\n\r\nThe fix is to convert the value to a string before checking if it only contains digits.\r\nLine 518 can therefore be changed as follows:\r\n\r\n```\r\nif ( ! ctype_digit((string) $this->cur_page) OR ($this->use_page_numbers && (int) $this->cur_page === 0))\r\n```\r\n\r\n","closed_by":{"login":"gxgpet","id":13217984,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjEzMjE3OTg0","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/13217984?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/gxgpet","html_url":"https://github.com/gxgpet","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/gxgpet/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/gxgpet/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/gxgpet/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/gxgpet/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/gxgpet/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/gxgpet/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/gxgpet/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/gxgpet/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/use